@startuml
title Dental Booking System - Complete Sequence Diagrams

== User Registration ==
autonumber
actor User
participant "Booking System" as System
database Database

User -> System: Register (name, telephone, email, password)
System -> Database: Store user details
Database --> System: Success
System --> User: Registration Confirmation

== User Login ==
autonumber
User -> System: Login (email, password)
System -> Database: Verify credentials
Database --> System: Authentication Success/Failure
System --> User: Login Response

== View Dentist List ==
autonumber
User -> System: Request dentist list
System -> Database: Fetch all dentists
Database --> System: Return dentists (name, experience, expertise)
System --> User: Display dentist list

== Book Appointment ==
autonumber
User -> System: Book Appointment (date, dentist_id)
System -> Database: Check availability
Database --> System: Available/Not Available
alt Appointment Available
  System -> Database: Create appointment
  Database --> System: Success
  System --> User: Booking Confirmation
else Appointment Not Available
  System --> User: Booking Failure
end

== View Own Booking ==
autonumber
User -> System: View my booking
System -> Database: Fetch user appointments
Database --> System: Return appointment details
System --> User: Display appointment

== Edit Own Booking ==
autonumber
User -> System: Edit Booking (reservation_id, new_date, new_dentist)
System -> Database: Update appointment details
Database --> System: Update confirmation
System --> User: Edit Success/Failure

== Cancel Own Booking ==
autonumber
User -> System: Delete Booking (reservation_id)
System -> Database: Remove appointment
Database --> System: Deletion confirmation
System --> User: Cancellation Confirmation

== Admin View All Bookings ==
autonumber
actor Admin
Admin -> System: View all bookings
System -> Database: Fetch all appointments
Database --> System: Return all appointment details
System --> Admin: Display all bookings

== Admin Edit Any Booking ==
autonumber
Admin -> System: Edit Booking (reservation_id, new details)
System -> Database: Update appointment
Database --> System: Update confirmation
System --> Admin: Edit Success/Failure

== Admin Delete Any Booking ==
autonumber
Admin -> System: Delete Booking (reservation_id)
System -> Database: Remove appointment
Database --> System: Deletion confirmation
System --> Admin: Delete Success/Failure

@enduml